des: How well do you know your other half? In this party game for friends or couples, players pair up to form a group. At the start of the game, Alexa quizzes each player on how well they know their friend or partner. The first player provides a response, and the second player in their group judges the responses. Get your group to the top and play today! Note: This skill was created using the Doubles Trouble Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
